results.title: Toasted Screenprinted Tshirt Womens Deep Scoop Neck for Layering Size Medium
results.description:
This "toasted" screenprinted tshirt is so darling and perfect for layering.  It is a beautiful chocolate brown with the text printed in tan colored ink. It indeed is toasted.   This tee has a deep scoop neck and is very feminine and flattering. It is fitted and is deliciously stretchy so it hugs your curves.

This shirt is a bella brand, size medium and measures at follows laying flat

Width at bust 13.50 inches
Width at waist 13 inches
Width at hip 14.25 inches

Need a different color, size or style of shirt, don't hesitate to contact me for options.  I can get a large variety and have them in stock in a few days.

Thanks for shopping at Teez Loueez. Click here to return to my shop: http://www.teezloueez.etsy.com
